ITEM NO.5                 COURT NO.11                  SECTION II-A
               S U P R E M E  C O U R T  O F  I N D I A
                       RECORD OF PROCEEDINGS
Petition for Special Leave to Appeal (Crl.) No. 9518/2025
[Arising out of impugned final judgment and order dated 19-05-2025
in CRA No. 4005/2025 passed by the High Court of Madhya Pradesh at
Indore]
RAHUL                                              Petitioner(s)
                                VERSUS
STATE OF MADHYA PRADESH & ANR.                     Respondent(s)
(FOR ADMISSION and IA No. 151438/2025 - EXEMPTION FROM FILING O.T.)
 
Date : 04-07-2025 This matter was called on for hearing today.
CORAM : 
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE M.M. SUNDRESH
         HON'BLE MR. JUSTICE K. VINOD CHANDRAN
(PARTIAL COURT WORKING DAYS BENCH)
For Petitioner(s) : 
                   Mr. S.K. Vyas, Sr. Adv.
                   Mr. Siddharth Sharma, AOR
                   Mr. Aditya Goyal, Adv.
                   Ms. Ishika Chauhan, Adv.                   
For Respondent(s) : 
          UPON hearing the counsel the Court made the following
                             O R D E R
Application for exemption from filing official translation of
Annexures P-1 to P-8, P-11 and P-12 is allowed.
Learned senior counsel appearing for the petitioner submits
that the chargesheet indicates that it is a case of suicide.
Issue notice.
(DEEPAK GUGLANI)                                 (POONAM VAID)
   AR-cum-PS                               ASSISTANT REGISTRAR
